channel.title: Need help with Jarring a webclient
channel.description:

[code=cpp]THIS BATCH IS FOR DEBUGGING THE EXECUTABLE JAR ONLY DOUBLE-CLICK THE "client.jar" TO RUN IT - Generated by: JAR Maker (http://www.goldenstudios.or.id/)

That happens when i Press Client.bat
and if i press Client.jar A Window will come up and it called "Java Virtual Machine Launcer"
Message (X) <- is a Icon Error: Invalid or corrupt jarfile C:\Users\#####\Desktop\client.jar
